#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a module for scheduling programs to run in the background. It is a "
"graphical user interface to <command>cron</command>, the &UNIX; system "
"scheduler."
msgstr ""
"To je modul za načrtovanje programov, ki se izvajajo v ozadju. To je "
"grafični uporabniški vmesnik za <command>cron</command>, sistemski "
"razporejevalnik &UNIX;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Don't forget to tell your system to start the <filename>crond</filename> "
"cron daemon first, or the settings in this module will not work."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite sistemu povedati, naj najprej zažene demona cron "
"<filename>crond</filename>, sicer nastavitve v tem modulu ne bodo delovale."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start Up"
msgstr "Zagon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start this module you will see a summarized view of existing "
"scheduled tasks and associated environment variables. If you are running as "
"the root user, you will see these items for all users on the computer as "
"well as the system scheduled tasks."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete ta modul, se prikaže povzetek obstoječih načrtovanih opravil in "
"povezanih okoljskih spremenljivk. Če ste zagnani kot uporabnik root, bodo ti "
"elementi prikazani za vse uporabnike v računalniku in sistemska načrtovana "
"opravila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>start up</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>start up</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>start up</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>start up</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduled Tasks"
msgstr "Razporejena opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scheduled tasks appear under a <guilabel>Tasks</guilabel> list. For each "
"scheduled task, the following items are displayed:"
msgstr ""
"Načrtovana opravila so prikazana na seznamu <guilabel>Opravila</guilabel>. "
"Za vsako načrtovano opravilo so prikazani naslednji elementi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduling"
msgstr "Razporejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this column either \"@reboot\" for task schedules at boot or the crontab "
"entry is displayed."
msgstr ""
"V tem stolpcu se prikaže \"@reboot\" za urnike opravil ob zagonu ali vnos v "
"crontab."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100 index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command"
msgstr "Ukaz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Program file and parameters."
msgstr "Programska datoteka in parametri."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:104 index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105 index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabled or Disabled."
msgstr "Omogočeno ali onemogočeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "A description for the task, such as its purpose."
msgstr "Opis naloge, na primer njen namen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduling Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti o načrtovanju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Natural language description of scheduled task."
msgstr "Opis razporejenega opravila v naravnem jeziku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment Variables"
msgstr "Spremenljivke okolja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Environment variables appear in the <guilabel>Environment Variables</"
"guilabel> list. For each environment variable, the following are displayed:"
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivke okolja so prikazane na seznamu <guilabel>Spremenljivke okolja</"
"guilabel>. Za vsako spremenljivko okolja so prikazani naslednji podatki:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:130 index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "Spremenljivka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable name."
msgstr "Ime spremenljivke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:134 index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Value"
msgstr "Vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable value."
msgstr "Vrednost spremenljivke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:142 index.docbook:180 index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment"
msgstr "Komentar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Natural language description of variable."
msgstr "Opis spremenljivke v naravnem jeziku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Environment variables appearing here will override any existing environment "
"variable for all scheduled tasks."
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivke okolja, ki so prikazane tukaj, bodo prevladale nad vsemi "
"obstoječimi spremenljivkami okolja za vsa načrtovana opravila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Scheduled Tasks"
msgstr "Uvrstitev opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new scheduled task, click the <guibutton>New Task...</guibutton> "
"button. Alternatively, you can select this action from the "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo načrtovano opravilo, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Novo "
"opravilo...</guibutton>. To dejanje lahko izberete tudi v kontekstnem meniju "
"<mousebutton>desnega</mousebutton> gumba miške."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Task Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Uredi opravilo"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Edit Task</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr "Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Spremeni opravilo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Edit Task</guilabel> dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Uredi opravilo</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the program. You can specify either a relative path or "
"absolute path. If you want to look up the program, click <guiicon>Browse</"
"guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ime programa. Določite lahko relativno ali absolutno pot. Če želite "
"poiskati program, kliknite ikono <guiicon>Brskaj</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a description of the task to schedule."
msgstr "Vnesite opis opravila za uvrstitev."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable this task"
msgstr "Omogočite to opravilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "To enable or disable the task, select or de-select this button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti ali onemogočiti opravilo, izberite ali odstranite izbiro "
"tega gumba."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run at system boot-up"
msgstr "Zaženi ob zagonu sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this button to run the task at system boot-up."
msgstr "Označite ta gumb, da bi zagnali opravilo ob zagonu sistema."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run every day"
msgstr "Zaženi vsak dan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to schedule the task to run daily, select this button."
msgstr "Če želite načrtovati dnevno izvajanje opravila, izberite ta gumb."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Months"
msgstr "Mesecev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the months during which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "Izberite mesece v katere bo opravilo razvrščeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Days of Month"
msgstr "Dnevi v mesecu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the days of the month on which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "Izberite dni v mesecu, v katere bo opravilo razporejeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Days of Week"
msgstr "Dnevi v tednu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the days of the week on which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "Izberite dneve v tednu, kamor bo opravilo uvrščeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hours"
msgstr "Ur"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the hours on which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "Izberite ure, za katere bo naloga načrtovana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minutes"
msgstr "Minut"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the minute at which the task is to be scheduled. <command>cron</"
"command> does not support scheduling tasks at smaller than one minute "
"intervals."
msgstr ""
"Izberite minuto, v kateri se bo opravilo načrtovalo. <command>cron</command> "
"ne podpira načrtovanja opravil v intervalih, manjših od ene minute."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:235 index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OK</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completes the creation of this task."
msgstr "Dokonča ustvarjenje tega opravila."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:240 index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancels the creation of this task."
msgstr "Prekine ustvarjenje tega opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select both days of the month, and days of the week, the task will "
"run when either condition is met. For instance, if you select the 1st and "
"15th, and select Sunday, the program will be run every 1st and 15th of the "
"selected months (regardless of day of week) as well as every Sunday of the "
"selected months (regardless of day of the month)."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete dneve v mesecu kot tudi dneve v tednu, bo opravilo pognano ko je "
"izpolnjen vsaj eden od obeh pogojev. Če na primer izberete 1. in 15. ter "
"nedeljo, bo program pognan vsakega 1. in 15. izbranega meseca (ne glede na "
"dan v tednu), kot tudi vsako nedeljo (ne glede na dan v mesecu)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scheduled task is not actually set up until the <filename>crontab</"
"filename> has been saved."
msgstr ""
"Opravilo v resnici ni razporejeno dokler ne shranite<filename>crontab</"
"filename>-a."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Scheduled Tasks"
msgstr "Upravljanje razporejenih opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with creating new tasks, changes to tasks will not actually be made until "
"the <filename>crontab</filename> is saved."
msgstr ""
"Kot velja pri ustvarjanju novih opravil, spremembe dejansko ne bodo veljale, "
"dokler ni <filename>crontab</filename> shranjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the buttons at the right of the task list to modify, delete, print or "
"run a selected task now. You reach all these actions from the context menu "
"as well. Additionally the context menu provides actions to cut, copy and "
"paste tasks."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbi na desni strani seznama opravil lahko spremenite, izbrišete, "
"natisnete ali zaženete izbrano opravilo. Vsa ta dejanja lahko izvedete tudi "
"v kontekstnem meniju. Poleg tega so v kontekstnem meniju na voljo dejanja za "
"izrezovanje, kopiranje in lepljenje opravil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Environment Variables"
msgstr "Dodajanje spremenljivk okolja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new environment variable, click the <guibutton>New Variable...</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo spremenljivko okolja, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Nova "
"spremenljivka...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can use the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"menu to choose this action."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje lahko izberete tudi z menijem <mousebutton>desnega</mousebutton> "
"gumba miške."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Variable dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Uredi spremenljivko"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo><guilabel>Edit Variable</guilabel> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <screeninfo><guilabel>Uredi spremenljivko</guilabel>.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase><guilabel>Edit Variable</guilabel> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno<phrase><guilabel>Uredi spremenljivko</guilabel>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the environment variable name. You can use the drop down list box to "
"select from the most common environment variables used by scheduled tasks. "
"Those include:"
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ime spremenljivke okolja. V spustnem seznamu lahko izberete "
"najpogostejše spremenljivke okolja, ki jih uporabljajo načrtovana opravila. "
"Med njimi so:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "HOME"
msgstr "HOME"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "To be used instead of the default user's home folder."
msgstr "Da se uporabi namesto privzete domače mape uporabnika."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "MAILTO"
msgstr "MAILTO"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To send email output to an email address other than the user's default email "
"address."
msgstr ""
"Za pošiljanje pošte na naslov, ki ni uporabnikov privzeti e-poštni naslov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "PATH"
msgstr "PATH"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "To be used to search folders for program files."
msgstr "Da se uporabi za iskanje programskih datotek v mapah."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "SHELL"
msgstr "SHELL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "To be used instead of the user's default value."
msgstr "Uporablja se namesto uporabnikove privzete vrednosti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "LD_CONFIG_PATH"
msgstr "LD_CONFIG_PATH"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of dynamic libraries. This allows cron jobs to execute "
"applications which have libraries they need to run installed outside the "
"system library path."
msgstr ""
"Lokacija dinamičnih knjižnic. To omogoča, da opravila cron izvajajo "
"aplikacije, katerih knjižnice, ki jih potrebujejo za zagon, so nameščene "
"zunaj poti do sistemske knjižnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the environment variable value."
msgstr "Vnesite vrednost spremenljivke okolja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a description for the environment variable, such as its purpose."
msgstr "Vnesite opis spremeljivke okolja, denimo njennamen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable this variable"
msgstr "Omogoči to spremenljivko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "To enable or disable the variable, select or de-select this button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti ali onemogočiti spremenljivko, izberite ali odstranite "
"ta gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completes the setting of this variable."
msgstr "Konča ustvarjenje tega opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancels the setting of this variable."
msgstr "Prekliče ustvarjanje tega opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The environment variable is not actually set up until the <filename>crontab</"
"filename> has been saved."
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivka okolja v resnici ni postavljena, dokler ni bil "
"<filename>crontab</filename> shranjen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Environment Variables"
msgstr "Upravljanje okoljskih spremenljivk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with creating new variables, changes to variables will not actually be "
"made until the <filename>crontab</filename> is saved."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri ustvarjenju novih spremenljivk, spremembe v resnici ne bodo "
"uveljavljene, dokler ni <filename>crontab</filename> shranjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the buttons at the right of the variable list to modify or delete a "
"selected variable. You reach all these actions from the context menu as "
"well. Additionally the context menu provides actions to cut, copy and paste "
"variables."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbi na desni strani seznama spremenljivk lahko spremenite ali izbrišete "
"izbrano spremenljivko. Vsa ta dejanja lahko izvedete tudi v kontekstnem "
"meniju. Poleg tega so v kontekstnem meniju na voljo dejanja za izrezovanje, "
"kopiranje in lepljenje spremenljivk."

